Inferno watched side eyed as the shot went over his head.  He felt 
something grab him from behind.  He squirmed for a mement then with 
one load pop his head inexplicably flew off and landed upsidedown on 
the control consel.
"Royal-" it said before shutting down.

Quickstrike just laughed at it all pointing to Inferno's head.
